replies.body:
Miss Fortune's pick rate is pretty good for her not previously being that popular. What I meant was like;

{{champion:33}} Top has one of the highest win rates at 54.75%. This win rate is actually pretty high, but we know that Rammus isn't overpowered. He only has a 0.32% pick rate and most people typically have around 130 games played on average with Rammus.

I just wanted to use the statistics without people complaining "oh its only because MF mains play her" when actually a lot of people in general are starting to play her now.

she requires a lockdown team to get the full duration of her ult most of the time
she doesn't bring much other then pure dmg and a slow if you look at some adcs that are meta right now
either they have
-a better overall mid/late game like {{champion:42}} /{{champion:18}} 
-bring more utility like {{champion:15}} and {{champion:429}}
